article.headline: Bailey's 18 lead Evansville past Tennessee Tech 82-51

images.name: Tennessee Tech Golden Eagles vs. Evansville Purple Aces: Full Highlights
images.caption: Tennessee Tech Golden Eagles vs. Evansville Purple Aces: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Bailey's 18 lead Evansville past Tennessee Tech 82-51
article.story: EVANSVILLE, Ind. -- — Chuck Bailey III's 18 points helped Evansville defeat Tennessee Tech 82-51 on Wednesday night. Bailey was 6 of 9 shooting and 4 of 4 from the free throw line for the Purple Aces (10-2). Ben Humrichous scored 15 points while going 5 of 6 (5 for 5 from 3-point range). Yacine Toumi had 10 points and finished 5 of 7 from the floor. David Early led the way for the Golden Eagles (5-8, Ohio Valley Conference) with 13 points. Jayvis Harvey added 12 points for Tennessee Tech. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
